3" width="2000"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 18:53:52 GMT</pubDate><title>Camp Mystic withdraws application to open this summer</title><updateDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 18:53:52 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Freddie Clayton</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 18:07:17 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>LONDON — As King Charles III closed out his four-day state visit to the U.S. on Thursday, President Donald Trump issued a three-word assessment of the monarch.“The greatest king,” Trump said after he and first lady Melania Trump said goodbye to Charles and Queen Camilla, an appraisal that explains why Charles could well be returning to the U.K. feeling a quiet sense of mission accomplished</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/europe/king-charles-trump-set-return-mission-accomplished-rcna342865</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/europe/king-charles-trump-set-return-mission-accomplished-rcna342865</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260430-charles-trump-mb-1659-86a5b6.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Samir Hussein</media:credit><media:text type="plain">King Charles III And Queen Camilla Wrap Up State Visit In Washington DC Area</media:text><media:description type="plain">King Charles and President Trump during a farewell ceremony at the White House on April 30, 2026.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260430-charles-trump-mb-1700-864b00.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Samir Hussein</media:credit><media:text type="plain">King Charles III And Queen Camilla Wrap Up State Visit In Washington DC Area</media:text><media:description type="plain">Trump bids King Charles III farewell outside the White House on Thursday.</media:descrip